<div id="outline-container-org13f28c7" class="outline-2">
<h2 id="org13f28c7"><span class="section-number-2">1.</span> Goal</h2>
<div class="outline-text-2" id="text-1">
<p>
Hello! We are a group of enthusiastic people wanting to solve the many problems around Bangla Natural Language Processing. We extensively focus on social inclusion and accessibility for universalism of human values.<br />
</p>


<div id="org3b95817" class="figure">
<p><img src="Goal/2022-11-18_13-00-08_iitlogo-blue.png" alt="2022-11-18_13-00-08_iitlogo-blue.png" width="200px;" /><br />
</p>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-orgf5ddd2f" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="orgf5ddd2f"><span class="section-number-3">1.1.</span> Contact Us</h3>
